  "text": "In the illusion that we now experience, it is difficult to maintain this response, especially if the entity's attack results in physical pain. But I assume that this response should be maintained even through physical loss of life or extreme pain. Is this correct? I am Ra. This is correct and further is of a major or principal importance in understanding, shall we say, the principle of balance. But rather fully imbued with love.",
